      • VitalStatus bulkImport(VitalSegment segment, java.io.InputStream inputStream)

        Imports the data in bulk mode. In case of indexeddb endpoint it only writes data to database, index is untouched (needs refresh). Import fails if there's any active transaction.

        throws:
        VitalServiceUnimplementedException
        throws:
        VitalServiceException
        Parameters:

        inputStream
        Returns:

      • VitalPipeline pipeline(groovy.lang.Closure<?> closure)

        Executes a mini-script in the service endpoint, all domain classes are available, if there's a domain with older version its classes also registered with NEW_ and OLD_ prefixes For convenience vitalsigns, this vitalservice are provided by the delegate. If the clsoure is wrapped with PIPELINE node the script object with closure will be returned instead for future use.

        Parameters:
        closure
        Returns:
        vitalpipeline instance if closure wrapped with PIPELINE, null otherwise
